Package cz.syntea.xdef.component Description

Provides tools for the X-components technology.

X-component is a Java class which is generated by the X-components technology (generated as the Java source code). Each X-component implements the interface XComponent.

  • GenXComponent

    Generator of Java source code of X-components (see GenXComponent).

  • XComponent

    Interface of XComponent classes (see XComponent).

  • XComponentUtil

    Static methods providing different tools used with X-components (see XComponentUtil).
